nodes.text: Yevethan breederies were places reserved for elite Yevetha. A Yevetha's mates would live in these breederies, waiting until they had their child. Nil Spaar, the Yevetha's darama, had a massive breedery during his tenure as head of the Duskhan League. Most breederies on Yevetha were destroyed by the Yuuzhan Vong.
